title: Base Camp Northcote
typeOfFood: Lacto, Indian, Take-out, Catering, Nepalese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Indian and Himalayan cuisine restaurant where the dishes in the vegetables section of the menu can be prepared vegan with the exception of the paneer (cheese) and kofta meals. Vegetable oil is used to cook all dishes. Vegan entrees can be deep friend in separate oil.
